      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' colspan=2><b><font color='#80000'>CORRECTION TO LG SHADOW SILK RECIPE</font>, By Watziz name</b><br><br>Lg Shadow Silk is 1 Silk, 2 Shadow Wolf skins/hides/pelts, and 1 Gather Shadows Necro spell.<br><hr size='1'></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' colspan=2><b><font color='#80000'>IN NERIAK AS WELL</font>, By Reeshl</b><br><br>This can be gotten in Neriak from any of the three sisters above the Commons gate - X'Tempi, X'Tompi, etc.  Frequently, I find these on their corpses once someone has come to kill them for exp, you may only carry or have one as it is a Lore item, so they slayers of these three Necro sisters can't grab more than one, so they haven't minded anyone picking it up - a LOT of DE newbie necs have this robe due to this - at least on Tarew Marr.<P>

Given the quantity of these available, I've only ever sold it for around 250-300pp.  Though have seen it listed for around 600pp, I think that would be in a different area of Norrath, certainly not in a zone where 2-3 pop up a day.

<br><hr size='1'></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' colspan=2><b><font color='#80000'>GOOD</font>, By Valerine of innoruuk</b><br><br>The information below is good so use it ! Good luck fellow Necromancers =)<br><hr size='1'></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' colspan=2><b><font color='#80000'>MISTAKE IN THIS ITEMS STATS.</font>, By Uzsuperbeast</b><br><br>The Robe of Enshroudment adds +4 to cold it doesn't take it away.<br><hr size='1'></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' colspan=2><b><font color='#80000'>NECRO QUEST</font>, By Talca yummyfoot</b><br><br>To get this robe you need to have good faction with the temple of solusek ro. The things you need are a werebat wing from werebats in unrest, a globe of shadow from nokta shamans in lower guk, a large shadowed silk (silk swatch-made of 2 spider silks,2 shadow wolf pelts, and a gather shadows spell). Lastly, you also need the mask of shadow from shadowed men (warning: the mask will disappear if you log out or get disconnected). Give all these things to the person (sorry forgot name) in the temple of solusek ro and you will receive the robe of enshroudment. It has a very cool all black look and looks especially great on gnomes. Good luck fellow necros!<br><hr size='1'></td>
